AddressInfo.Title: Say When Casino
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Charger located on left side of wall at west entrance.

GeneralComments: 75A 208V (15 kW) J1772 Charger located on left side of wall at west entrance. Parking in this area is reserved for EV and tour buses. Family friendly place to stop and charge. Casino 24 hours, cafe open 6 am - 9 pm. Espresso, bar, cafe, slots, wifi. EV charger donated by Tim Hastrup, with installation costs paid by Bowers Wealth Management. A second 15 kW charger has been installed Spring of 2019 thanks to Bowers Wealth Management. Free electricity courtesy of the Say When Casino.
